## Critical Files - DO NOT MODIFY WITHOUT PLAN

| File | Status | Purpose |
|------|--------|---------|
| `qwen_unified_live.py` | 🔒 FROZEN | Main bot (30-day validation) |
| `whale_monitor.py` | 🔒 FROZEN | Whale signal generation |
| `macro_filter.py` | 🔒 FROZEN | Macro state tracking |
| `config.json` | ⚠️ Params only | Strategy parameters |
| `.env` | 🔒 NEVER COMMIT | API credentials |
| `CLAUDE.md` | ✅ Reference | Operational guide |
| `whale_wallets.json` | ⚠️ 3 wallets monitored | Configuration |

## Mandatory Checks Before Implementation

- [ ] Read CLAUDE.md first (project status)
- [ ] Read DEVELOPMENT_PROCESS.md (workflow rules)
- [ ] Check git status (no uncommitted changes)
- [ ] Verify .env exists locally (NEVER commit)
- [ ] Understand 30-day validation plan (ongoing since 2026-04-10)

## After Every Change

```bash
# 1. Test changes
pytest test_*.py

# 2. Update PROJECT_STATUS.md with changelog
# 3. Verify no secrets in git diff
git diff --no-color | grep -i "key\|secret\|password" || echo "OK"

# 4. Commit with conventional message
git commit -m "feat/fix/refactor: description"

# 5. Clean up session
/clear
```

## Risk Management - Sacred Rules

- **Max position size**: 40% of equity
- **Max drawdown before halt**: 15%
- **Consecutive loss limit**: 5 trades → stop trading
- **Leverage**: 1.0x only (no margin)
- **Live account**: $211.19 (small, validate on paper first)

**Any change affecting these MUST go through full Brainstorm → Plan → Review cycle.**

## When Context > 70%

1. Save progress (git commit)
2. Run `/clear`
3. Start new session
4. Check CLAUDE.md for project status
5. Continue with fresh context budget

## Switching Between Environments

| From | To | Action |
|------|-----|--------|
| Claude Code CLI | Cursor IDE | Review CLAUDE.md + DEVELOPMENT_PROCESS.md |
| Cursor IDE | Claude Code CLI | Same (both read CLAUDE.md) |
| Any | External LLM | Reference AGENTS.md + AGENT_INSTRUCTIONS.md |

All environments share: CLAUDE.md, DEVELOPMENT_PROCESS.md, CONTEXT_MANAGEMENT.md

## Key Metrics to Track

- **Session Context Usage**: Monitor via status line (target: <50%)
- **Token Efficiency**: CLAUDE.md should save 27x tokens per session start
- **Process Adherence**: Every task should follow Brainstorm→Plan→Implement→Review cycle
- **30-Day Validation**: Track `trade_alignment_log.json` entries

